            "text": "‚ÄúThe United States relies on consent-by-registration statutes [like the Pennsylvania law] to obtain personal jurisdiction over various foreign entities,‚Äù said Keller. ‚ÄúIf it‚Äôs unconstitutionally coercive when Pennsylvania does it, why isn‚Äôt it unconstitutionally coercive when the United States does it?‚Äù",
